
Simple 3-step installation:

% ./configure
% make
% sudo make install


Possible options for configure:

--disable-async-exec		doesn't do anything!?
--disable-tty-ctl		TTY_CTL
--disable-viewers		VIEWERS
--disable-history		HISTORY
--disable-rt-sched		ALLOW_RT_SCHED
--disable-gui			INTERFACE
--disable-stepit		STEPIT
--disable-numrec		HAVE_NUMREC
--disable-sound			HAVE_SOUND
--disable-debug			DEBUG
--disable-cautious		CAUTIOUS
--disable-avi			doesnt do anything!?


PACKAGES NEEDED FOR BUILDING UNDER REDHAT/CENTOS

freeglut-devel
mesa-libGLU-devel
openmotif-devel
alsa-lib-devel
curl-devel
matio-devel
libtiff-devel
libjpeg-devel
ffmpeg-devel
gsl-devel
ncurses-devel
libdc1394-devel
texinfo-tex
libtermcap-devel
opencv-devel
kernel-devel	(for building nvidia driver)
